{"tid":93951,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人長期鼻塞？","createTime":"2017-01-24T23:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T13:15:12.000Z","uid":76036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38edb5673eb00fecaf45e2afeac292d333c0e42c","tid":93951,"uid":76036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:20:13.000Z","msg":"近呢兩年開始長期鼻塞，已經依賴左通鼻既藥水<br />\n訓個陣唔用既話好辛苦淨係用口抖氣完全訓唔到<br />\n有無人有相似經驗 已經係鼻炎 又懶去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbd1ce5877aad84177670cc609cc032bf19602f","tid":93951,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:21:28.000Z","msg":"搵唔搵倒原因"},{"pid":"818cea1476f7d389460dd0ce73f2162f60cad8dd","tid":93951,"uid":61403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:22:16.000Z","msg":"塞左四年，影響唔大冇睇醫生"},{"pid":"2ec5246d921b1559913f0f453c73cf39f4f50619","tid":93951,"uid":76036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵唔搵倒原因</blockquote><br />\n主因應該係一開始受唔住去左買藥水去通<br />\n到而家依賴左越來越嚴重"},{"pid":"85ee0bf10266661c69c73f7b494e721f5c612a06","tid":93951,"uid":76036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:27:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>塞左四年，影響唔大冇睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n因為無影響到你訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家我訓前都要噴一下，但藥效得幾粒鐘，過左就會醒一醒要在噴先訓返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2eaeac67a43538d6af959304e8debb41af03d35","tid":93951,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:28:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵唔搵倒原因</blockquote><br />\n主因應該係一開始受唔住去左買藥水去通<br />\n到而家依賴左越來越嚴重</blockquote><br />\n有冇用過生理鹽水洗鼻"},{"pid":"19b39e87f54070478170f2ce04010ad80c0a9454","tid":93951,"uid":76036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搵唔搵倒原因</blockquote><br />\n主因應該係一開始受唔住去左買藥水去通<br />\n到而家依賴左越來越嚴重</blockquote><br />\n有冇用過生理鹽水洗鼻</blockquote><br />\n有睇過下，試過一兩次，但始終要keep住用先有效果，加上一開始用根本無作用咁，我又堅持唔到一直用鹽水，始終一開始勁辛苦好難忍"},{"pid":"85f4c81b24ce9497210f75fa71a49ae0bb9a0ef2","tid":93951,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:34:02.000Z","msg":"要睇醫生"},{"pid":"aeac5cc74203c2ba679fc6d62d310f668f5eecb5","tid":93951,"uid":76036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:35:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n應該要做小手術"},{"pid":"76bfea4b05d9e6d6b8b61e72de1b05ae4db2879b","tid":93951,"uid":7245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以後勸力換床單"},{"pid":"58ef5a2640670462cb00e9188df1b6a15dcadd3a","tid":93951,"uid":76036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:38:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以後勸力換床單</blockquote><br />\n關咩事？"},{"pid":"262c02accd7a2bb4d6cad51326d624717d96805c","tid":93951,"uid":61403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:40:07.000Z","msg":"有冇睇過有冇息肉"},{"pid":"113d915662ae3bdcf0b8389fc6cff48f68b52da0","tid":93951,"uid":76036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:43:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇睇過有冇息肉</blockquote><br />\n唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f71b02862870bbd4b8cc52fce548106a474b303","tid":93951,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:45:57.000Z","msg":"近兩年鼻水倒流+鼻塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日都好似有野塞住個喉嚨，講野聲又變咗<br />\n睇醫生開啲抗敏感收鼻水hea鳩我"},{"pid":"4d68e829a08f7d24d816264d0271179523b5b2ff","tid":93951,"uid":76036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近兩年鼻水倒流+鼻塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\"