T00:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近呢兩年開始長期鼻塞，已經依賴左鼻既藥水<br />\n訓個陣唔用既話好辛苦淨係用口抖氣完全訓唔到<br />\n有無人有相似經驗 已經係鼻炎 又懶去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nd藥水多數有類固醇 會做成依賴同會影響中樞神經<br />\n你應該發炎 要斷尾又唔想做手術 睇中醫喇 但要好有恆心同錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabec85a83ad1c19c6d302627f7334c6a683084a","tid":93951,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>近呢兩年開始長期鼻塞，已經依賴左鼻既藥水<br />\n訓個陣唔用既話好辛苦淨係用口抖氣完全訓唔到<br />\n有無人有相似經驗 已經係鼻炎 又懶去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nd藥水多數有類固醇 會做成依賴同會影響中樞神經<br />\n你應該發炎 要斷尾又唔想做手術 睇中醫喇 但要好有恆心同錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發炎啲鼻水/涕唔係應該黃色綠色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我啲透明偏白嘅"},{"pid":"80ad8cf0e2be1523daa3d3f4981359ed326f66a7","tid":93951,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:17:23.000Z","msg":"搞左長期塞一邊"},{"pid":"e3471862bcd7f72eff3a1482ad5415a295766f6c","tid":93951,"uid":47797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:17:47.000Z","msg":"出世塞到現在 聽講要做手術 但無咩大影響就唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b46edbc447391564895fe3ac64a30a2a93b3eb","tid":93951,"uid":42041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:21:27.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人成日感冒鼻塞訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以買左通鼻劑日日用<br />\n點知過左一排發現到個感冒好返佢都繼續塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然後尾戒左<br />\n不過個鼻都係長期塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a913ec3d4f54e2fbdc399874010cc79aa8ccc04","tid":93951,"uid":76036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人成日感冒鼻塞訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以買左通鼻劑日日用<br />\n點知過左一排發現到個感冒好返佢都繼續塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然後尾戒左<br />\n不過個鼻都係長期塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你介到咪好"},{"pid":"517960535899fcfb1aa0540dbf7fa88b0234d11b","tid":93951,"uid":42041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:30:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人成日感冒鼻塞訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以買左通鼻劑日日用<br />\n點知過左一排發現到個感冒好返佢都繼續塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然後尾戒左<br />\n不過個鼻都係長期塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你介到咪好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戒到都係塞果度衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日因爲咁訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓到咁上下就會咁為個口乾晒自己醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出去飲完水就訓唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4041dfba3c4d6f73a1e52c75ebc1ea7ae32eb415","tid":93951,"uid":76036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:35:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人成日感冒鼻塞訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以買左通鼻劑日日用<br />\n點知過左一排發現到個感冒好返佢都繼續塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然後尾戒左<br />\n不過個鼻都係長期塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你介到咪好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戒到都係塞果度衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日因爲咁訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓到咁上下就會咁為個口乾晒自己醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出去飲完水就訓唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼你可以都叫訓得著，我唔用既話真係成晚眼光光之餘仲要塞哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58fe5f36e0a94864b1d5da6eff1ec7cb5dc16442","tid":93951,"uid":6992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:39:26.000Z","msg":"一坐低同訓低就塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b480dc642640984198328a4fbf71a5d9d1af58f","tid":93951,"uid":77529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:42:39.000Z","msg":"搵日去睇耳鼻喉專科啦。我自己都係鼻塞去睇，發現有鼻息肉。醫生叫我唔好用市面上安鼻靈等收縮血管嘅噴鼻，會愈來愈依賴，而且會反彈（唔噴仲塞）。佢開左鼻敏感藥+類固醇噴鼻（鼻眼適），呢家冬天keep住每晚噴一次，舒服好多。"},{"pid":"f982768097573a0dc223749bc98e4d72fcb56d32","tid":93951,"uid":42041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你介到咪好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戒到都係塞果度衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日因爲咁訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓到咁上下就會咁為個口乾晒自己醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出去飲完水就訓唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼你可以都叫訓得著，我唔用既話真係成晚眼光光之餘仲要塞哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我最開頭都係訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長期係咁個人好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想整整佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0bf8004b5d38cd39d06c9311145cceec762a43","tid":93951,"uid":67719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>近呢兩年開始長期鼻塞，已經依賴左鼻既藥水<br />\n訓個陣唔用既話好辛苦淨係用口抖氣完全訓唔到<br />\n有無人有相似經驗 已經係鼻炎 又懶去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nd藥水多數有類固醇 會做成依賴同會影響中樞神經<br />\n你應該發炎 要斷尾又唔想做手術 睇中醫喇 但要好有恆心同錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發炎啲鼻水/涕唔係應該黃色綠色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我啲透明偏白嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以你形容<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我覺得</strong></span>係鼻竇發炎<br />\n你試下去睇中醫先喇 西醫除左手術之外都係治標唔治本 你長期用類固醇既藥更加只係好似hi野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbb2cea3a48e34393b6ee027e79432e8bfc7d10","tid":93951,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:51:33.000Z","msg":"我有一邊鼻成日都多鼻屎到塞住，另一邊又唔淨氣成日鼻塞，搞到有陣時訓訓下教窒息醒左走去撩鼻屎+sun鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0facd94404bf20b20f88ab9119a73290a74ac3","tid":93951,"uid":35089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T00:51:48.000Z","msg":"做運動有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975f9b0264bf8618f4ba34f77cb4fc3dbac0d945","tid":93951,"uid":67719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T01:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做運動有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定有用 但要睇空氣質素 去郊外行下山幾好<br />\n我細個都成日係咁 多數係發炎 坐底訓底怒流鼻水<br />\n訓覺長時間流就會變倒流<br />\n跟住搞到口龍都發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800aba3606c6689478e1ce6831cb7f8eb442725c","tid":93951,"uid":76036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T02:04:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵日去睇耳鼻喉專科啦。我自己都係鼻塞去睇，發現有鼻息肉。醫生叫我唔好用市面上安鼻靈等收縮血管嘅噴鼻，會愈來愈依賴，而且會反彈（唔噴仲塞）。佢開左鼻敏感藥+類固醇噴鼻（鼻眼適），呢家冬天keep住每晚噴一次，舒服好多。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過真係懶去睇 我可能都係同你相似，不過發覺香港真係幾多人有鼻既問題 d空氣質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f3512c0c90eb7192d681a7a42e967bfa1d8c70","tid":93951,"uid":71217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T02:21:31.000Z","msg":"睇過醫生，淋巴腫左定唔知點，要做手術，但無做，每日塞過紅隧。日日用噴鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a065f223299e26a24e6ff23d1d62aadcc0cc15f6","tid":93951,"uid":6221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T02:24:42.000Z","msg":"其實洗鼻真心work"},{"pid":"3d0b9549a42e3f08caa349a6a138d07159c3dc18","tid":93951,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都有呢啲困擾 之後用左安鼻靈薄荷嘅嗰隻舒緩咗好多 兩邊鼻都通曬瞓覺都好咗</blockquote><br />\n無用，吸完都通唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4231be762200c6f30b42baab2196b4b050fee5e3","tid":93951,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"真係頂唔順先用通鼻劑，<br />\n用完會好眼訓，日日都單孔做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d15c168c0024bbbf3be9c62e2a47f0d1813b67d","tid":93951,"uid":76036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}